---
import Link from "../components/link.astro";
import Subpage from "../layouts/subpage.astro";
import Typography from "../layouts/typography.astro";
---

<Subpage
  description="A brief rundown of the what, why, and who of the NBA Surprise Teams Tracker"
  title="Info"
>
  <Typography class="mx-auto px-4 lg:max-w-[60%]">
    <h1 class="text-center font-title text-2xl text-lime-400 md:text-4xl">
      What is the NBA Surprise Teams Tracker?
    </h1>
    <p class="text-2xl text-green-200">
      Alex Speers and Andrew Schlecht host <span class="italic"
        >The Saturday Slam N' Jam,</span
      > the Saturday episode of <span class="italic">The Athletic's</span> NBA podcast.
      Each year, they run a segment called Surprise Teams. If you want to get up
      to speed straight from the source, here's the introductory episode for the
      2024-2025 season (segment starts at the 8:15 mark):
    </p>
    <iframe
      allow="autoplay *; encrypted-media *; fullscreen *; clipboard-write"
      class="mx-auto"
      height="175"
      sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation"
      src="https://embed.podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/embiid-extension-surprise-teams-pelicans-preview/id1358187061?i=1000670194276"
      style="width:100%;max-width:660px;overflow:hidden;border-radius:10px;"
      title="The Athletic NBA Daily podcast, 9/20/2024 â€” Embiid Extension + Surprise Teams + Pelicans Preview"
    ></iframe>
    <p class="text-2xl text-green-200">
      If you're short on time, though, a team qualifies as a Surprise Team if:
    </p>
    <ul class="text-2xl text-green-200">
      <li>Their preseason over/under is below 36 wins</li>
      <li>They beat their over/under by at least 10 games</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-2xl text-green-200">
      This site just keeps track of how well the current season's Surprise Team
      candidates are doing at, well, surprising us.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-center font-title text-2xl text-lime-400 md:text-4xl">
      Who are you?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-2xl text-green-200">
      My name's Zack McCartney. I'm a web programmer and basketball fan with a
      possibly troubling amount of time on my hands. Thanks for stopping by!
    </p>
    <p class="text-2xl italic text-green-200">
      (And to be totally clear: entirely unaffiliated with Alex, Andrew, the
      Athletic / NYT, and the NBA; random guy working solo.)
    </p>
    <p
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 text-2xl text-green-200 md:flex-row"
    >
      <Link class="text-xl" href="mailto:zack@grepco.net">zack@grepco.net</Link>
      <Link class="text-xl" href="https://www.grepco.net" target="_blank"
        >https://www.grepco.net</Link
      >
    </p>
  </Typography>
</Subpage>
